<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Bad Listener -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Brutality_Always.label>油盐不进</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Brutality_Always.label>
  <!-- EN: Forget a silver tongue; this pawn won't take no for an answer. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Brutality_Always.description>什么三寸不烂之舌，这个角色压根不听"不"字。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Brutality_Always.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Coin flip -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Brutality_High.label>看心情动手</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Brutality_High.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn only respects consent half the time. The other half, its prey better get ready for a fight. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Brutality_High.description>这个角色只有一半的时间会尊重对方的意愿。剩下那一半嘛，猎物最好做好干一架的准备。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Brutality_High.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Rare -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Brutality_Low.label>不常动粗</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Brutality_Low.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn is even less inclined than most to use violence for persuasion. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Brutality_Low.description>这个角色比大多数人更不倾向于用暴力来说服别人。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Brutality_Low.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Peaceful -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Brutality_Never.label>和平主义者</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Brutality_Never.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn wouldn't use violence to coerce its prey if a proposal was turned down. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Brutality_Never.description>即使提议被拒绝，这个角色也绝不会用暴力胁迫猎物。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Brutality_Never.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Normal -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Brutality_Normal.label>正常尺度</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Brutality_Normal.label>
  <!-- EN: Most of the time this pawn wouldn't think of fighting to vore any prey that wasn't interested. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Brutality_Normal.description>大多数时候，这个角色不会考虑用武力来吞食不感兴趣的猎物。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Brutality_Normal.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Vore eagerness -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_ProposalFrequency_High.label>吞食热心</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_ProposalFrequency_High.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn will propose vore on its own more often than other pawns. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_ProposalFrequency_High.description>这个角色会比其他人更频繁地主动提出吞食邀请。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_ProposalFrequency_High.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Vore disinterest -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_ProposalFrequency_Low.label>吞食冷淡</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_ProposalFrequency_Low.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn will seek vore out on its own much less frequently than others. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_ProposalFrequency_Low.description>这个角色主动寻求吞食的频率远低于其他人。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_ProposalFrequency_Low.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Vore apathy -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_ProposalFrequency_None.label>吞食漠然</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_ProposalFrequency_None.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn does not care enough about vore to initiate vore proposals on its own. It has no qualms about being told to do it, though. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_ProposalFrequency_None.description>这个角色对吞食提不起兴趣，不会主动发起吞食邀请。不过别人让它吞，它倒也没什么意见。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_ProposalFrequency_None.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Passing vore interest -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_ProposalFrequency_Normal.label>吞食随兴</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_ProposalFrequency_Normal.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn proposes vore as frequently as everyone else. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_ProposalFrequency_Normal.description>这个角色发起吞食邀请的频率和普通人差不多。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_ProposalFrequency_Normal.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Vore obsession -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_ProposalFrequency_VeryHigh.label>吞食痴迷</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_ProposalFrequency_VeryHigh.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn is ever-eager for vore, and will propose it on its own twice as much as other pawns. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_ProposalFrequency_VeryHigh.description>这个角色对吞食永远充满热情，主动发起邀请的频率是其他人的两倍。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_ProposalFrequency_VeryHigh.description>
  
</LanguageData>